{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, we will organize the, the-- with the Jewish authorities, here in England, we will organize this side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, of course, you guys over there have to organize your side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time-- and I learnt this only weeks ago, on the occasion of seeing a film that was, it's called Kindertransport, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was shown here in Washington, just, just a few weeks ago, in early '97.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were some people from the-- some of the young professionals that had been thrown out of their professional-- out of the professions.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of the people from the Jewish community authorities got together, made up some committees that had to work very fast.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And don't forget, this was all-- they were definitely under the gun, as far as time was concerned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they knew that it couldn't be much longer, with the war coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- and, oh, they had to get the agreement of the Germans, number one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They did get it, for-- somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how much money that cost, but-- how many bribes it cost.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the details had to be negotiated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Who should go, how to handle the applications, how to let people know that this exists-- all the myriad administrative details. 'Administrative detail' was a-- is a term that, lucky for me, at that time I did not even know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've learnt in the meantime what it means.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But at that time, all these things were just totally beyond me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's why I use the term 'miracle.' In a way, it was a kind of miracle.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
